  <entry>
    <title>洛谷P1017-进制转换</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/07/15/%E6%B4%9B%E8%B0%B7P1017-%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/07/15/%E6%B4%9B%E8%B0%B7P1017-%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%B6%E8%BD%AC%E6%8D%A2/</id>
    <published>2021-07-14T18:03:22.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-07-16T13:53:29.919Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>想试着在高三毕业后的漫长暑假里恢复当年作为OIer的实力，结果做了好久才做出这么一道普及/提高-的题……我啥时候堕落成这个样子了艹</p><span id="more"></span><h3 id="题意概括"><a href="#题意概括" class="headerlink" title="题意概括"></a>题意概括</h3><p>给定一个十进制数<strong>n</strong>，将其转化为<strong>r</strong>进制数。其中<strong>r</strong>为负数。若<strong>r</strong>≤-10，则按照十六进制的转化规则表示数字。例如，将15转化为-2进制，则得到的数为：110001。</p><h3 id="题目分析"><a href="#题目分析" class="headerlink" title="题目分析"></a>题目分析</h3><p>先考虑<strong>r</strong>为正数的情景：分析十进制数本身，我们如果要将十进制数转化为十进制数，则可以对原数不断除以10，保存其余数并倒序输出以得到结果。拓展一下，不难发现，对于任意正进制<strong>r</strong>，我们都可以使得原数不断除以r，保存余数倒序输出来获取转化后的数。</p><p>那么负进制呢？首先需要知道的是，<strong>假设有两个异号数A和B，则A%B的结果为abs(A)%abs(B)的相反数</strong>。负进制数进行相同的操作，可以发现余数有时会变成负数，而显然我们不能在某个数位上添加一个负数。因此，需要对负数进行处理。</p><p>已知：<strong>被除数÷除数=商…余数</strong>，通过简单的数学变换，我们可以得到：<strong>商*除数+余数=被除数</strong>。此时余数和除数均为负数。那么此时，为了让余数变为正数，我们可以让商增加1，即增加一份除数，再使得余数的值变为其本身减去除数。这样做可以使得我们得到的新式与原式等同，而由于<strong>余数必定小于除数，因而余数-除数一定是正数</strong>。操作方式为：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++">余数-=除数;<br>商+=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>此外，当<strong>r</strong>&gt;10时，我们需要将每个数位上大于十的数字转化为字母A、B、C……。在这里，笔者使用了映射表的形式进行转化（别问为什么，我知道map效率很低但是我就是想用它）：</p><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp">map&lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">char</span>&gt; switchNum;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">register</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">30</span>; i++) &#123;<br>switchNum[i + <span class="hljs-number">10</span>] = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span> + i;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h3><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="hljs-meta-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">inline</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">read</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">register</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">char</span> c = <span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br><span class="hljs-keyword">register</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> f = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, _ = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (c &gt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span> || c &lt; <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>)<br>f = (c == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>) ? <span class="hljs-number">-1</span> : <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, c = <span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (c &lt;= <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; c &gt;= <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>)<br>_ = (_ &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">3</span>) + (_ &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) + (c ^ <span class="hljs-number">48</span>), c = <span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br><span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> _ * f;<br>&#125;<span class="hljs-comment">//快速读入</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> n, r;<br>map&lt;<span class="hljs-keyword">int</span>, <span class="hljs-keyword">char</span>&gt; switchNum;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> pNote[<span class="hljs-number">21</span>];<span class="hljs-comment">//记录每一位上的值</span><br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//freopen(&quot;test.txt&quot;, &quot;r&quot;, stdin);</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">register</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">30</span>; i++) &#123;<br>switchNum[i + <span class="hljs-number">10</span>] = <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span> + i;<br>&#125;<br>n = <span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>(), r = <span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> saveN = n;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> p = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (n != <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> tempA = n % r;<br>n /= r;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (tempA &lt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) &#123;<br>tempA -= r;<span class="hljs-comment">//操作余数</span><br>n += <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//操作商</span><br>&#125;<br>pNote[p] = tempA;<br>p++;<br>&#125;<br>cout &lt;&lt; saveN &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;=&quot;</span>;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-keyword">register</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">int</span> i = p - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &gt;= <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i--) &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (pNote[i] &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">9</span>)<br>cout &lt;&lt; pNote[i] ;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">else</span><br>cout &lt;&lt; switchNum[pNote[i]];<br>&#125;<br>cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;(base&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; r &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;)&quot;</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;想试着在高三毕业后的漫长暑假里恢复当年作为OIer的实力，结果做了好久才做出这么一道普及/提高-的题……我啥时候堕落成这个样子了艹&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
